Node.js is a running javascript on the server.
It is a javascript runtime.
It is built on Chrome's V8 Javascript engine.
Node Js REPL- It is a feature to do experiment on nodeJsand debug Js it too. You can called it as JS cmd
Read, Eval, Print, Loop
To start REPL in your terminal 
just write node and then enter


REPL
1. Js expression
2. use varriables
3. multiLine code
4. use(_) to get the last result
5. editor mode //.editor


Node.Js core module
module is same as javascript libraries. It gives some power that can help in making application easily and desinging.

core module are built in module.
